<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.8.5">
<l>kaḻalmaṉṉar cūḻak katirpōl viḷaṅki</l>
<l>yeḻaluṟṟu mīṉṭē yiruntuṉṉai nōkkuñ</l>
<l>cuḻalaip perituṭait tuccō taṉaṉai</l>
<l>yaḻala viḻittāṉē yaccōvaccō</l>
<l rend="indent">vāḻiyaṅ kaiyaṉē yaccōvaccō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who gazed hotly at the very deceitful Duryodhana,</l>
<l>who, shining like the sun</l>
<l rend="indent">while surrounded by kings with warrior’s anklets,</l>
<l>saw you, began to depart, returned, and sat down! Oh! Oh!</l>
<l>He who bears the discus in his hand! Oh! Oh!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
